title: 6 AM Hour - He Had Legos EVERYWHERE
description:
Falen officially leaves for Spain today and will be back next week! Dave is not on the show today as he's probably recovering from the partying he did at the Paul McCartney Concert in Boston last night, He'll be back on the show tomorrow though!

Jenny's First Song of the Day: I Took A Pill In Ibiza - Mike Posner, Worst Date Wednesday Replay, & More!
